Amendment to Implementing Regulation (EU) No 532/2011
Implementing Regulation (EU) No 532/2011 is amended as follows:
(a) in the title, the words ‘Alpharma Belgium BVBA’ are replaced by ‘Zoetis Belgium SA’;
(b) in the second column of Annex I, the words ‘Pfizer Ltd’ are replaced by ‘Zoetis Belgium SA’;
